<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="http://weibo.com/1694816142 等我考完研就回来" class="zu-question-my-bio"><a href="http://weibo.com/1694816142" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">weibo.com/1694816142</span><span class="invisible"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a> 等我考完研就回来</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="8">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kalafiction" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kalafiction" class="zg-link" title="KalaFiction">KalaFiction</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qian-yu-hua" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qian-yu-hua" class="zg-link" title="千羽桦">千羽桦</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shadowluo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shadowluo" class="zg-link" title="爆爆影">爆爆影</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2033995" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>汉语相对于英语，有固定的<strong>调值，</strong>汉语用<strong>五度标记法</strong>来标记调值（我们可以近似得把他们看成五个音高不同的音符）具体如下：</p><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/9729c8f42147a848a484cf06f6347a30_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="570" data-rawheight="401" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="570" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/9729c8f42147a848a484cf06f6347a30_r.jpg"><p>现代汉语四声分别是 <strong>阴平、阳平、上声及去声，</strong>他们的调值分别是 阴平（55），阳平（35），上声（214），去声（51）。</p><p>所以有外国人听汉语的时候会觉得就像是听音乐一般，大家可以把一句汉语里面的每个音都转变为调值，然后试着在钢琴上（<a href="http://www.4399.com/flash/100983_3.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">我爱弹钢琴小游戏,<i class="icon-external"></i></a>）快速弹奏出来听一听，看和普通话语音像不像。</p>
<a href="/question/24629780/answer/34774136" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
